Executive
Summary
Drapius Capital Africa Limited is a
premier investment & project management
firm headquartered in Kampala, Uganda.
We function as a strategic bridge between visionary entrepreneurs and
the global capital required to bring life-changing ideas to scale.
By integrating investment sourcing, brand development, and full-scale
project implementation, we ensure that sustainable development in
East Africa is not just a goal, but a measurable reality.
Background &
History
Founded by Drake Makanga and Pius Walugembe, Drapius
Capital was established to address the critical funding gap faced
by high-impact entrepreneurs in Africa. Recognizing that brilliant
ideas often fail due to a lack of market entry strategy and financial
backing, our founders built a firm that offers more than just capital
—we offer a pathway from concept to consumer.
Legally registered in Uganda and operating from our head offices
at Buganda Road Block 663, we have cultivated a vast network of
business corporations and private investors committed to the
growth of the African continent.
Vision &
Misson
To be the leading catalyst for sustainable economic
transformation in East Africa, recognized for turning innovative
ideas into market-leading institutions that empower communities.
Mission
Vision
To source, secure, and manage strategic investments for
high-impact projects while providing the branding and
