market success.
Strategic Aims
& Objectives
The primary aim of Drapius Capital is to create a self-sustaining
ecosystem where African
innovation meets global capital. We ensure that capital creates a
measurable impact and a
profitable return.
To serve as a launchpad for East African
entrepreneurs, transforming brilliant
ideas into viable, profit-generating
enterprises that create jobs.
To champion the UN Sustainable
Development Goals (SDGs) by
prioritizing investments that solve critical
social and environmental
challenges.
To build the necessary branding and
distribution "pipes" so that great local
products reach the final consumer.
To provide international investors with a
secure, transparent, and locally-informed
entry point into the East African market.
